    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-size: 9pt; font-style: italic;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Уй-жойни сотишга ишончнома</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ишончнома тасдиқланган сана </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган ЖИЭМ жойлашган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да жойлашган </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган ЖИЭМ номи ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> муассасаси</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган ЖИЭМ жойлашган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ҳудудида жойлашган </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган ЖИЭМ номи ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сонли ЖИЭ муассасида жазони ўтаётган маҳкум – </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Ишончнома берувчининг туғилган йили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Ишончнома берувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Ишончнома берувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#13}Ишончнома берувчига паспорт берган ИИБ (ҳудуд)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Ишончнома берувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">йилда берилган) ушбу ишончнома билан </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Ишончнома олувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да яшовчи – </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Ишончнома олувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Ишончнома олувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Ишончнома олувчига паспорт берган ИИБ (ҳудуд)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Ишончнома олувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган) ўзимга тегишли бўлган </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Сотилиши бўйича ишонч билдирилган уй-жой жойлашган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">манзилда жойлашган хонадонни ўзи хоҳлаган шартлар ва нархда сотишига ваколат бераман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Менга тегишли мазкур хонадонни сотишга қаршилик қилувчи турмуш ўртоғим йўқлиги ҳақида ҳам менинг номимдан ариза ёзишига ваколат бераман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ушбу ваколатни бажариш учун менинг номимдан тегишли ташкилотларда, шу жумладан, ҳокимликларда, солиқ ва Давлат солиқ қўмитаси ҳузуридаги Кадастр агентлигида, нотариал идораларда вакилим бўлишга, маълумотномалар олишга ва топширишга, ариза ёзишга ва имзо кўйишга, нотариал идорада олди-сотди шартномасини тузишга ва имзолашга, сотилган хонадон учун пулни олишга ва ушбу ишончнома билан боғлиқ бўлган барча ҳаракатларни бажаришга ҳуқуқ бераман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ишончнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#23}Ишончнома неча йил муддатга берилган</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йил муддатга, бошқа шахсга ўтказиш ҳуқуқисиз, яъни </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#24}Ишончноманинг амал қилиши тугайдиган кун</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">гача берилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ишончноманинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 141-142-моддалари мазмуни менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, ишончноманинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ишончнома берувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>______________ Имзо</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ушбу ишончномани мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган ЖИЭМ жойлашган манзил </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да жойлашган </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган ЖИЭМ номи ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ЖИЭ муассасаси бошлиғи </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}ЖИЭМ раҳбарининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> тасдиқладим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ишончномага маҳкум </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Ишончнома берувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">менинг ҳузуримда имзо қўйди. Унинг шахси аниқланди, муомалага лаёқатлилиги текширилди. Шахсий мулоқот давомида унинг муомалага лаёқатлилиги шубҳа туғдирмади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ишончнома рўйхатга олиш китобининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Ишончнома рўйхатга олиш китобининг қайд қилинган варақ</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> - сонли бетида </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Ишончнома рўйхатга олиш китобига қайд қилинган рақам</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">–<span class=\"leading\"></span>сон билан рўйхатдан ўтказилди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ЖИЭМ раҳбари </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}ЖИЭМ раҳбарининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>______________ Имзо</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>М.Ў.</span></p>\n</div></div>",
